name: Barbell Bench Press
description: A compound exercise that primarily targets the chest, shoulders, and triceps by pressing a barbell from a lying position.

name: Incline Barbell Bench Press
description: A bench press variation performed on an incline to emphasize the upper chest and shoulders.

name: Dumbbell Bench Press
description: A chest exercise using dumbbells for increased range of motion and muscular engagement.

name: Pull-Ups
description: A bodyweight exercise that strengthens the back and biceps by pulling the body up to a bar.

name: Lat Pulldown
description: A machine-based exercise that mimics the pull-up, focusing on developing the lats and upper back.

name: Barbell Row
description: A barbell exercise that strengthens the mid-back, lats, and rear delts.

name: Deadlift
description: A powerful compound movement that targets the back, legs, and core while improving overall strength.

name: Overhead Barbell Press
description: A pressing movement that builds shoulder strength and stability while engaging the triceps.

name: Dumbbell Shoulder Press
description: A variation of the overhead press using dumbbells for improved range of motion and control.

name: Lateral Raises
description: An isolation exercise that strengthens the lateral deltoids for broader shoulders.

name: Barbell Bicep Curl
description: A mass-building bicep exercise using a barbell for heavier resistance.

name: Hammer Curl
description: A variation of the bicep curl that also targets the forearms and brachialis.

name: Triceps Pushdown
description: A cable machine exercise that isolates and strengthens the triceps.

name: Skull Crushers
description: A triceps extension movement that helps build size and strength.

name: Squat
description: A fundamental compound movement that targets the quads, hamstrings, and glutes.

name: Leg Press
description: A machine-based leg exercise that isolates the quads, hamstrings, and glutes.

name: Lunges
description: A unilateral leg exercise that strengthens the quads, hamstrings, and glutes.

name: Leg Curl
description: A hamstring-focused machine exercise that strengthens the posterior chain.

name: Leg Extension
description: An isolation exercise that strengthens the quadriceps by extending the knee.

name: Calf Raise
description: An exercise that strengthens the calves by raising the heels off the ground.

name: Plank
description: An isometric exercise that strengthens the core, shoulders, and stabilizer muscles.

name: Hanging Leg Raises
description: A core exercise performed while hanging from a bar, engaging the lower abdominals.

name: Russian Twists
description: A rotational core exercise that targets the obliques.

name: Battle Ropes
description: A conditioning exercise that builds upper body endurance by moving heavy ropes in various patterns.

name: Kettlebell Swing
description: A dynamic movement that builds explosive power in the hips and posterior chain.

name: Tire Flips
description: A strongman-style movement that develops power by flipping a heavy tire.

name: Pallof Press
description: An anti-rotation exercise that enhances core strength and stability.

name: Dumbbell Snatch
description: A power movement that involves explosively lifting a dumbbell from the ground to overhead.

name: Farmers Carry
description: A loaded carry exercise that improves grip, core stability, and endurance.
